'''印度国家图书馆'''（{{lang-bn|'''ভারতের জাতীয় গ্রন্থাগার'''}}）是一所位于加尔各答[[贝尔韦代雷府|贝尔韦代雷府]]中的图书馆。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url = http://www.nationallibrary.gov.in/nat_lib_stat/useful_info.html|title = Useful Information|date = |accessdate = |website = National Library|publisher = |last = |first = |ref = nlinfo|archive-date = 2018-12-26|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181226023810/http://www.nationallibrary.gov.in/nat_lib_stat/useful_info.html|dead-url = yes}}</ref>按照容积和公共纪录来看，它是印度最大的图书馆。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thecolorsofindia.com/interesting-facts/miscellaneous/largest-library-in-india.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-05-09 |archive-date=2018-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226023809/http://www.thecolorsofindia.com/interesting-facts/miscellaneous/largest-library-in-india.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://education.oneindia.in/news/2011/12/16/progress-to-be-made-in-the-national-library-kolkata.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-05-09 |archive-date=2018-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181226023815/https://www.careerindia.com/news/2011/12/16/progress-to-be-made-in-the-national-library-kolkata.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ndl.go.jp/en/cdnlao/newsletter/047/473.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-04-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407064259/http://www.ndl.go.jp/en/cdnlao/newsletter/047/473.html |archivedate=2014-04-07 }}</ref>印度国家图书馆由印度政府的文化旅游部管辖。图书馆用来收集，传播和保存印度发行的资料。其藏书超过220万册。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kolkata.clickindia.com/tourism/nationallibrary.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-04-01 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407083037/http://kolkata.clickindia.com/tourism/nationallibrary.html |archivedate=2014-04-07 }}</ref>在印度独立之前，这是曾是孟加拉副州长的官邸。

